A: I'm not sure what you are asking, but I think you are asking how to extract two elements from a stream by their positions.
If that is the case, then you can use the skip method to skip the first two elements and then use the findFirst method to get the first element.
List<String> strings = Arrays.asList("s0", "s1", "s2", "s3", "s4");
String s0 = strings.stream().skip(0).findFirst().get();
